item.description:
An Tua Nua is a great venue, not too far from the Fenway/Kenmore area, which has karaoke on wednesday nights! It's a nice bar with good food, and they have salsa wednesday nights in the neighboring room so there's something for everyone! We had a fantastic time there in May, and hope you guys will be able to join us this time around! ***note, there's no cover for the karaoke, but there's a $7 cover for the salsa...***

Hope to see you there, whether you're singing or cheering on the singers!

C line to St Mary's St, first stop after Kenmore.
item.how_to_find_us: must sign up for the meetup to find out!
